synopsis: In a desolate park, where crime is on the rise, a young man attempts to assault an innocent women. However, his crimes will soon be matched in a fight to the death
tagline: Titus beats up a woman, then gets his shit rocked

titre: Tattness: The Other Side of Hell: The Documentary
synopsis: The Documentary outlines the rise to success of Keith "Tattness" McCleary. From growing up in an abusive home to living on the streets to achieving success and becoming friends with so many well known celebrities. A tale of true hardship that will make you be inspired, cry and laugh. This is a story you do not want to miss.
